# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:（喺投資、賭博或生意中）為咗防止損失擴大而將持有嘅資產或賭注賣出或放棄（量詞：次）
eng:to cut losses
<eg>
yue:佢見股價一直跌，就決定止蝕離場。 (keoi5 gin3 gu3 gau3 jat1 cit3 daak3, zau6 ding6 hak1 zi2 sai6 lei5 ceoi2 coeng4.)
eng:Seeing the stock price keep falling, he decided to cut his losses and exit the market. [end of text]


